text.text: Situated at a central location which is very accessible by MRT or bus, this library also boosts of a huge collection of books. There are five levels here catering to different audiences for each and you can spend a lazy afternoon here while reading books.

text.text: Atmosphere wonderful, huge library and large range of fab books. My fave library! It could use some more space for the kids section tho.
